Hey! Following <a href="http://www.hortont.com/racarr/?p=27">Robb's</a> recent blog post about an implementation of Life as a GLSL shader, I now present to you a Mac OS X screensaver in the same style (using his shader and the original <a href="http://www.mikeash.com/?page=software/gpulife/">GPULife</a> source).

